caption: I often take my friends to this place with my highest recommendations. I visit this place often. I get very good feedback from my friends. I visited this restaurant on 2/2/19 . The gentleman at the register was unfriendly. My friend and I decided to dine in although it was cold inside. Realizing the cold air was coming from the bathroom, me The customer pulled the bathroom door. I mentioned it to the gentleman at the register and he said nothing. My tortilla was cold and hard and when I spoke to him he mentioned my complaint to the woman who prepared the food. She was not pleased and rolled her eyes. I had planned on ordering food to go, but changed my mind. I'd like to say thanks to the unpleasant food and bad attitude we found a real Mexican Restaurant around the corner (Rancho Alegre). Manuel treated us with respect and the food we purchased to go was amazing!

Other noticeable changes is they redid the floors with light tiling and now offer coffee. Workers that day (might be the new owner) was very friendly as well.
